The paper discusses security and privacy concerns in the context of Mobility as a Service (MaaS), which involves the integration of various transportation services into a single platform. This falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) as well as cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the coordination of resources among different providers, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
